        <item>
            <title>Google Pixel 8 Pro / 8 推出　AI 修圖 + 阻攔 Spam Call + 7 年系統升級</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/05/google-pixel-8-pixel-8-pro/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-pixel-8-pixel-8-pro</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/05/google-pixel-8-pixel-8-pro/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Oct 2023 05:50:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197438</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Google 於其年度「Made By Google」新品發布會推出 Pixel 8 及 Pixel 8 Pro 兩款新智能旗艦手機。新機結合 Bard 人工智能，全面引入 AI First 技術，並且大幅提升相機的性能。</p><p>新 Pixel 8 及 Pixel 8 Pro 機殼採用緞面金屬飾面、拋光玻璃背板和回收材料製成，設有海灣藍、米白、霧灰、玫瑰粉與黑色 5 款顏色可供選擇。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.31.57-1-694x438.png" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.31.57-1-694x438.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.31.57-1-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.31.57-1-768x485.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.31.57-1-1536x970.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.31.57-1.png 1542w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.23-694x496.png" alt="" width="694" height="496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.23-694x496.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.23-1260x900.png 1260w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.23-768x549.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.23.png 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.29-694x454.png" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.29-694x454.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.29-1280x838.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.29-768x503.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.29.png 1524w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.35-694x505.png" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.35-694x505.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.35-1236x900.png 1236w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.35-768x559.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.35.png 1382w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.40-694x508.png" alt="" width="694" height="508" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.40-694x508.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.40-1229x900.png 1229w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.40-768x562.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.33.40.png 1330w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Pixel 8 Pro 配備 6.2 吋 Actua 顯示熒幕，比上片 Pixel 7 的顯示熒幕亮度高 42%。而其背面設有新温度感測器，可讓用快速掃描物體以獲取其温度，並可透過 Pixel 的温度計應用程式保存到 Fitbit 中。</p><p>Google Pixel 8 及 Pixel 8 Pro 的相機系統有大升級。 Pixel 8 配備具有 f/1.68 大光圈的 5000 萬像素廣角鏡、82mm 鏡頭視野和 1/1.31 英吋感測器，而 Pro 亦配備了相同的主鏡頭，同時都配備了新的微距對焦模式。</p><p>但兩者相機系統之間最大的區別是 8 Pro 配備了 4800 萬像素 Quad PD 感應器、f/1.95 光圈超廣角鏡及 4800 萬像素 f/2.8 光圈 5X 光學長焦鏡頭，並改進了自動對焦性能。而且 Pixel 8 Pro 獨享「夜視錄影」功能，能提升夜間錄影的畫質表現。</p><p>新 Pixel 手機獨設魔術修圖工具，透過生成式 AI 技術，可以消除背景的路人和物件，更可以將主體移位，以及可自行消除背景噪音或放大影片音量的音效功能。另外，新「Best Take」功能則是用於拍攝團體照片的新 AI 功能，可以捕捉每一名人物的最佳表情，並自動合成一張照片。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197447 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.05-694x517.png" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.05-694x517.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.05-768x572.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.05.png 1088w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外，新「Call Screen」同樣採用 AI 技術，可幫助用家平均減少 50% 的垃圾廣告電話。Google 亦首度為 Pixel 8 提供長達 7 年的安全性更新與作業系統版本的升級，以及 Feature Drop 軟件支援。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197448 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.17-694x419.png" alt="" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.17-694x419.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.17-1280x773.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.17-768x464.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-05-13.36.17.png 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Google Pixel 8 起價為 699 美元（約港幣＄5,472 元），Google Pixel 8 Pro 則起價為 999 美元（約港幣＄7,821 元）。如現預訂 Pixel 8 Pro，買家更可同時免費獲得 Pixel Watch 2 而不另收費。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1197457" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cap2245.jpg" alt="" width="630" height="515" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://blog.google/products/pixel/google-pixel-8-pro/">blog.google</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
