        </item>
        <item>
            <title>壽司郎新技術改善衞生，測試 1.5 米長屏幕虛擬迴轉帶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/05/sushiro-trial-virtual-band-with-long-screens/hottopic/food/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sushiro-trial-virtual-band-with-long-screens</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/05/sushiro-trial-virtual-band-with-long-screens/hottopic/food/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Oct 2023 02:47:27 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[飲食]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[壽司郎]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[迴轉壽司]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197384</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信大部分食客對迴轉壽司的認知，就是一碟碟壽司在輸送帶上迴轉，食客可以按喜好和需要在輸送帶拿取想食的壽司。這個安排可能會在未來有所改變，大型連鎖迴轉壽司店壽司郎早前宣佈，將會在日本 3 間門市測試新技術，以觸控螢幕取代迴轉輸送帶，讓食客可以點選想要的壽司款式。</p><p><span id="more-1197384"></span></p><p>這款虛擬迴轉輸送帶由一塊 50cm 高，闊 150cm 的顯示屏幕組成，並且安裝在每張枱旁邊。顯示器的畫面會模仿一般迴轉輸送帶，各式壽司和食品會由畫面一邊慢慢流向另一邊，食客可以點擊畫面的圖像下單，情況與從迴轉帶拿取壽司類似，分別是點選的壽司會從通往每張枱的管道送達。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_29764"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h3L5_ZVYoCg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>壽司郎表示會以東京新宿西口店、大阪吹田市江阪店和名古屋市天博燒山店作為試點，測試上述的虛擬迴轉輸送帶。雖然有媒體認為壽司郎是應對近期發生的多宗惡搞事件，減少壽司在迴轉帶上被幹擾，但壽司郎社長新井晃平解釋試驗新技術與 COVID-19 疫情爆發後，顧客變得更注重衞生有關。他們認為透過加入新技術可以新的方式呈現迴轉壽司的樂趣，亦讓這傳統能夠得以傳承，為食客提供更愉快的用餐體驗。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASR9W5F4XR9WULFA00P.html?ref=tw_asahicom">asahi</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
